          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0367P0-04388'>
        <a name='S6CV0367P0_20010425_WH_116'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-john-hutton' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0367P0_20010425_WH_116' title='Link to this speech by Mr John Hutton' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
