          <p class='first-para'>
            No, I will not give way. It is time that the hon. Gentleman addressed the reality. I know that Conservative Members do not like it up them. <span class="italic">[Interruption.]</span> Everyone heard the hon. Gentleman's contribution. The hon. Member for Romsey, who did a very good job, would probably back me up if I asked her to. The hon. Gentleman said that the real problem was that we were not funding social services adequately. When Conservatives are confronted with their record on the issue, and their conspicuous failure even to match the present level of spending that this Government have committed to social services&#x2014;
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0367P0-04391'>
        <a name='S6CV0367P0_20010425_WH_119'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-tim-loughton' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0367P0_20010425_WH_119' title='Link to this speech by Mr Tim Loughton' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
